Class Fence

  • java.lang.Object
    • Rectangle
      • Fence

  • public class Fence
extends Rectangle
    This class extends the Rectangle class. The Fence class exists of a Rectangle (and a triangle - planned) to create a picket-fence like shape, over which the user should jump.
    See Also:
    Rectangle, Sheep
